\c 8
\s Zvipo zvakaunganidzirwa varombo
\p
\v 1 Zvino tinokuzivisai, hama, nyasha dzaMwari dzakapiwa pamakereke eMakedhonia;
\v 2 kuti pakuedzwa kukuru kwedambudziko, kuwanzwa kwemufaro wavo neurombo hwavo hwakadzama zvakawedzera pafuma yekupa kwavo.
\v 3 Nokuti vaiva vane chido pakukwanisa \add kwavo\add*, ndinopupura, kunyange kupfuura kukwanisa \add kwavo\add*,
\v 4 nechikumbiro chikuru vakatigombedzera, kuti tigamuchire chipo uye kugovana parubatsiro rwunova rwevatsvene;
\v 5 uye kwete sezvatakatarisira, asi vakatanga kuzvipa ivo kuna Ishe, nekwatiri nechido chaMwari.
\v 6 Zvekuti takakurudzira Tito, kuti sezvaaiva ambotanga, saizvozvo apedzisewo kwamuri basa iri renyashawo.
\v 7 Asi sezvamakawanza pazvese, parutendo, uye pashoko, uye paruzivo, uye pakushingaira kwese, uye parudo rwenyu kwatiri, \add tarirai\add* kuti muwanzewo pabasa iri renyasha.
\v 8 Handitauri semurairo, asi nekushingaira kwevamwe uye ndichiidza uchokwadi hwerudo rwenyu.
\v 9 Nokuti munoziva nyasha dzaIshe wedu Jesu Kristu, kuti kunyange aiva akafuma, nekuda kwenyu wakava murombo, kuti imwi kubudikidza neurombo hwake mufume.
\v 10 Zvino pachinhu ichi ndinopa maonero; nokuti ichi chinokubatsirai, imwi makatotanga kubva gore rakapera, kwete kuita chete, asi nekuda.
\v 11 Asi ikozvinowo pedzisai kuita, kuti, sezva\add pan\add*e chishuwo chemoyo, saizvozvo \add kuripo\add* kupedzisawo kubva pane zva\add mu\add*nazvo.
\v 12 Nokuti kana chishuwo chemoyo chiripo, munhu anogamuchirika zvichienderana nezvaanazvo, kwete kuenderana nezvaasina.
\v 13 Nokuti hakusi kuti vamwe vave nekurerusirwa, imwi muremerwe;
\v 14 asi kubva pakuenzana, panguva yaikozvino zvakawanda zvenyu \add zviwedzere\add* pakushaiwa kwavo, kutiwo zvakawanda zvavo \add zviwedzere\add* pakushaiwa kwenyu, kuti kuve nekuenzana,
\v 15 sezvazvakanyorwa \add zvichinzi\add*: Waka\add unganidza\add* zvizhinji haana kuva nezvakasara; newaka\add unganidza\add* zvishoma haana kushaiwa.
\p
\v 16 Asi ngaavongwe Mwari wakaisa mumoyo maTito kushingaira kwakadaro kwamuri,
\v 17 kuti zvirokwazvo wakagamuchira kurudziro, asi zvaaiva achishingaira zvikuru, wakabva akaenda kwamuri nechido chake.
\v 18 Zvino takatuma pamwe naye hama, rumbidzo yake muevhangeri yakagura nemumakereke ose;
\v 19 zvisati zviri \add izvozvo\add* chete, asi wakasarudzwawo nemakereke kuti atiperekedze nenyasha idzi, dzakabatiswa nesu mukurumbidzwa kwaIshe uyu, nechishuwo chemoyo wenyu;
\v 20 tichidzivirira izvi, zvimwe umwe angatimhura pamusoro pezvipamhidzirwa izvi zvinobatiswa nesu;
\v 21 tichirangarira zvakanaka kwete pamberi paIshe chete asi pamberi pevanhuwo.
\v 22 Uye takatuma navo hama yedu, yatakawana yakashingaira pazvizhinji kazhinji, asi zvino anonyanya kushingaira nekuda kwekukuvimbai kukuru.
\v 23 Kana zviri zvaTito, umwe wangu nemushandi pamwe neni kwamuri; kana hama dzedu, nhume dzekereke, \add vari\add* kukudzwa kwaKristu.
\v 24 Naizvozvo ratidzai kwavari uchapupu hwerudo rwenyu nehwekuzvikudza kwedu pamusoro penyu, nepamberi pemakereke.